title: Vehicle strikes security barrier near White House: Secret Service
text:
Vehicle strikes security barrier near White House: Secret Service Friday, February 23, 2018 - 00:31 
A passenger vehicle struck a security barrier near the White House on Friday, but did not breach the White House complex, the U.S. Secret Service said in a series of tweets. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
